track_notes: Via Old Baldy Trail and Super Trail, plus a 0.7 mile scramble up steep, dense, and very thorny terrain.
Down Track.  The first 0.7 miles i steep and dense, thorny terrain.

This is a loop hike that hits 2 10-point summits.  There is a very tough bushwhack section of roughly half-mile from Super Trail to the Josephine summit, otherwise the hike is on well established trails.  Plan a very long day if you do this hike!
track_title: Loop to Josephine Peak and Mt Wrightson
